name: Your Letter
description:
***
ALL THE LETTERS A-Z ARE AVAILABLE!
JUST SEND ME A NOTE WITH THE LETTER YOU WANT AND THE BACKGROUND COLOR YOU PREFER: LIGHT BLUE, LIGHT PINK OR LIGHT YELLOW
***

There's a little world living on your favourite letter, where a gentle wind blows away leaves and small red apples and where little animals spend the time having tea and looking around...

*

Print of one of my original illustrations from the "The Living Alphabet" serie.

The printed area measures 18cm x 21cm (7.1" x 8.3") and is off-centered on a A4 sheet leaving a white border for framing.

The illustration is laser printed on 250 gsm Paper.

The print is signed and dated. It will be packaged with care.
